Web Content Extraction Benchmark - Extended Version

This project is based on the original Web Content Extraction Benchmark:
  Copyright 2023 Janek Bevendorff
  Repository: https://github.com/chatnoir-eu/web-content-extraction-benchmark
  License: Apache License 2.0

Original Paper:
  "An Empirical Comparison of Web Content Extraction Algorithms"
  Bevendorff et al., SIGIR 2023
  DOI: 10.1145/3539618.3591920

Modifications and Extensions:
  - Added BLEU metric evaluation
  - Integrated Crawl4AI extraction model
  - Extended datasets: Canola and Newspaper3k

This project uses Crawl4AI library:
  Repository: https://github.com/unclecode/crawl4ai
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Used for web content extraction via WebScrapingStrategy and DefaultMarkdownGenerator

